    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "That's a very intense way to frame it. If the debate is actually between people who want to minimize risk and people who want to maximize human potential through rapid progress, shouldn't a policy advisor at least outline the merits of both approaches fairly? Or is the \"safety\" side just objectively the correct one?",
